<span class="margnote"><span id="an_014">dan 7:14</span></span>

him

([Dan 7:13](../../../bib/kjv/dan007.htm#013).md); ([Dan
7:14](../../../bib/kjv/dan007.htm#014).md) is identical with ([Rev
5:1-7](../../../bib/kjv/rev005.htm#001).md) and antedates the fulfilment of
